item.title: C01
item.description:
Classic Series – Evergreen Box Combos

1. Elegant Album Cover
2. Matching Designer Box
A premium album and matching box combo, both featuring large acrylic panels on the cover and lid for a bold, modern look. The big acrylic pieces provide striking coverage, giving the set a sleek, high-end finish that makes your memories stand out beautifully.
